g.text: Vector LSM (YugabyteDB abstraction for vector indexing libraries)
- Manages multiple in-memory and on-disk vector indexes built with external libraries
- Exposes APIs to insert/search vectors to higher layers of DocDB
- Maintains in-memory vector index and flushes it to disk once it fills up
- On the read path, merges TopK across all persisted indexes and in-memory buffers
- Vector index compactions: combines index files while discarding deleted vectors.
